        >
            Expertos en diseñar miradas que cautivan. Llevamos la experiencia de
            un <strong class="text-white font-medium">estudio de lujo</strong> a la
            comodidad de tu hogar.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Buttons with shimmer -->
        <div
            class="hero-buttons flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 md:gap-5 justify-center px-2"
        >
            <button
                onclick="window.open('https://wa.me/56975598631?text=Hola,%20quisiera%20reservar%20una%20cita.', '_blank')"
                class="btn-primary group relative overflow-hidden bg-evolve-accent text-white px-7 md:px-10 py-3.5 md:py-4 rounded-full font-bold shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(197,160,101,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(197,160,101,0.5)] transition-all duration-500 transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 cursor-pointer text-sm md:text-base shimmer-hover"
